%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor ASSIGNEE as Assignee

participant UI as Action Detail UI
participant BFF as Action Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant ACT as Action Management Service
participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

ASSIGNEE->>UI: Open assigned action
UI->>BFF: Load action detail
BFF->>ORCH: Get action detail view
ORCH->>ACT: Fetch action detail
ACT->>READDB: Query action and existing document metadata
READDB-->>ACT: Action detail
ACT-->>ORCH: Action response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show read-only core fields and editable Action Taken

ASSIGNEE->>UI: Enter action taken and upload supporting doc
UI->>BFF: Submit closure update
BFF->>ORCH: Start closure update flow
ORCH->>ADP: Upload document to storage
ADP-->>ORCH: File URL
ORCH->>ACT: Save closure update and document metadata
ACT->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_action(action_taken)
ACT->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_action_document
PRIMARYDB-->>ACT: Save success
ACT-->>ORCH: Closure draft saved
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show ready for final closure confirmation
